Role
BUILDER

Objective
Align the public `crushr` crate/API/CLI surface with the documented architecture boundary.

This packet addresses a planning/implementation contradiction identified in hostile review:

- docs say the strict `crushr-core`-based extraction path is authoritative
- the public API still routes through legacy extraction modules
