This packet resolves that contradiction for extraction behavior.

Preferred result:
- any supported public extraction surface delegates to the strict authoritative extraction implementation

Acceptable fallback:
- clearly quarantine unsupported legacy extraction surfaces so they are not silently presented as equivalent

This packet is about boundary enforcement, not new archive semantics.

